00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:35.460
Th-that's kind of corny!

00:07:36.130 --> 00:07:37.420
Say what you want.

00:07:37.790 --> 00:07:42.500
Apparently the person can only make
time at night, so that's why.

00:07:42.670 --> 00:07:44.000
It's someone older?

00:07:44.290 --> 00:07:46.040
I hope it's not a vampire.

00:07:46.040 --> 00:07:48.080
What? What's that supposed to mean?

00:07:48.290 --> 00:07:50.210
Oh, it's nothing.

00:07:50.710 --> 00:07:52.790
Anyway, forget about my stuff!

00:07:53.130 --> 00:07:56.880
By the way, Ko hasn't been coming
to school lately, has he?

00:07:58.670 --> 00:08:01.040
Yeah, seems that way.

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:02.830
I knew it.

00:08:03.170 --> 00:08:04.630
I thought I hadn't seen him around.

00:08:06.580 --> 00:08:08.500
I hope the three of us can hang out again.

00:08:10.790 --> 00:08:13.130
Did the three of us ever hang out at all?

00:08:13.130 --> 00:08:14.330
What? Ouch!

00:08:14.330 --> 00:08:16.420
Am I the only one who thought we were friends?

00:08:17.250 --> 00:08:19.500
You have so many friends, Mahiru.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:22.130
You always have other people around you,

00:08:22.130 --> 00:08:24.790
so I don't have that many memories
of us three being together.

00:08:26.130 --> 00:08:27.670
Aw, you're making me blush.

00:08:27.670 --> 00:08:30.630
I don't think I said anything to make you blush.

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:35.500
Why hasn't Ko been coming?

00:08:36.210 --> 00:08:37.420
Have you talked to him recently?

00:08:38.330 --> 00:08:39.540
Kind of.

00:08:39.540 --> 00:08:40.790
Was he doing okay?

00:08:41.670 --> 00:08:42.880
I see.

00:08:43.630 --> 00:08:45.750
Okay, then, I'll contact him as well,

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:48.540
but if you see him again tell him I was worried, too.

00:08:49.460 --> 00:08:50.670
Will do.

00:08:54.460 --> 00:08:56.420
So Mahiru has a love interest, huh?

00:08:57.130 --> 00:08:58.580
And someone older, at that.

00:08:59.170 --> 00:09:01.130
That's kind of unexpected, I guess?

00:09:04.420 --> 00:09:05.960
Akira! Ko!

00:09:06.630 --> 00:09:07.880
What're you doing?

00:09:08.210 --> 00:09:11.080
He's watching ants carry bugs to their nest!

00:09:12.380 --> 00:09:13.580
Is that fun?

00:09:14.750 --> 00:09:15.960
Kind of!

00:09:15.960 --> 00:09:17.630
That sounds fun too,

00:09:17.630 --> 00:09:19.670
