00:09:54.630 --> 00:09:56.170
If it isn't Yamori-kun!

00:09:56.170 --> 00:09:57.420
'Sup?

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:05.000
Huh? Who do you mean?

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:07.250
