00:10:12.130 --> 00:10:14.830
By the way, I heard your blood's mad tasty?

00:10:14.830 --> 00:10:16.290
I'm so intrigued!

00:10:16.290 --> 00:10:17.580
You totally intend to drink it!

00:10:19.250 --> 00:10:21.080
So how were things after that?

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:22.290
Any progress?

00:10:25.250 --> 00:10:26.790
I'm not sure what to do.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:33.420
To become a vampire,
I have to fall in love with Nazuna-chan,

00:10:33.420 --> 00:10:37.210
and I meant to do that
no matter how many years it took, but...

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.500
The one year limit.

00:10:39.500 --> 00:10:41.710
So now that won't work anymore.

00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:48.130
Nazuna-chan's stance is to
go ahead and do what I want,

00:10:48.130 --> 00:10:50.710
but she's not going to actively turn me into a vampire.

00:10:51.380 --> 00:10:53.330
I have to figure it out.

00:10:53.790 --> 00:10:55.460
I have to be the one to change.

00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:57.500
But...

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.210
