00:11:01.380 --> 00:11:02.580
To like someone...

00:11:03.460 --> 00:11:05.420
To fall in love, what is that like?

00:11:09.710 --> 00:11:12.670
<i>H-holy crap!</i>

00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:16.170
<i>A pure and innocent middle schooler asking,
"What is love like?"</i>

00:11:16.170 --> 00:11:17.540
<i>Ahhhh!</i>

00:11:17.540 --> 00:11:19.380
<i>Is this for real?</i>

00:11:19.380 --> 00:11:21.040
<i>I can't even!</i>

00:11:26.380 --> 00:11:28.250
I-I see...

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:30.960
Right!

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:33.960
Just leave it to Love Master Kikyo Seri-chin
to help you out!

00:11:34.750 --> 00:11:36.790
"Love Master Seri-chin"...

00:11:36.790 --> 00:11:40.380
Here's a surefire way for a guy and girl to get closer...

00:11:41.540 --> 00:11:44.170
Nazuna-chan, let's go on a date!

00:11:44.170 --> 00:11:45.380
