Wh-what? That's so not true!

00:12:39.210 --> 00:12:40.710
Don't be so stubborn.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:43.630
You know I understand you more than anyone.

00:12:43.630 --> 00:12:45.250
I hate you, okay?!

