00:12:54.630 --> 00:12:58.540
Why else would you choose a romcom, then?

00:12:58.540 --> 00:13:01.920
All I can do is clench my face muscles
and try to stay sane!

00:13:02.170 --> 00:13:05.000
S-sorry, shall we leave?

