Tell me, Ko-kun.

00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:18.580
What is a date, exactly?

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:25.630
Is this a date?

00:15:26.580 --> 00:15:30.210
Then we're always going on dates, aren't we?

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:31.580
Denshinbashira no neiki ga
Telephone poles snoozing<b></b>

00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:32.540
Just do what you always do.

00:15:31.580 --> 00:15:34.210
Kansen douro no akubi ga
Highways yawning<b></b>

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:35.210
I find that pretty fun.

00:15:34.210 --> 00:15:36.790
Utatane shita jihanki ga
Vening machines dozing<b></b>

00:15:36.790 --> 00:15:39.500
Shizuke ni kanaderu
A quiet meloday<b></b>

00:15:39.630 --> 00:15:42.080
Shingouki no matataki
Traffic lights flashing<b></b>

00:15:42.080 --> 00:15:44.790
Gaitou no saeta me ga
Streetlamps with wakeful eyes<b></b>

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:47.380
Mado ga kobosu itonami ga
Windows glowing with life<b></b>

00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:50.210
Kirakira terashiteru
They glimmer and illuminate<b></b>

00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:55.960
<b>8th Night: All of Us</b>

00:15:52.420 --> 00:15:54.040
To the next place, let's go!

00:15:54.040 --> 00:15:55.460
So we are going!

00:15:58.330 --> 00:16:01.130
That idiotic vampire!

00:16:01.130 --> 00:16:03.080
I only took my eyes off her for like a second!

00:16:03.540 --> 00:16:04.830
Next place, next place!

00:16:04.830 --> 00:16:06.170
Yeah, let's go!

00:16:06.170 --> 00:16:07.710
Beer, beer!

00:16:08.290 --> 00:16:09.000
So where should we go?

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:10.000
Whaddaya mean?
So where should we go?<b></b>

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.210
The usual place, of course.

00:16:11.210 --> 00:16:12.830
Beer! Beer!

00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:17.250
What? We're not going to karaoke?

00:16:17.540 --> 00:16:19.080
I wanna get something to eat.

00:16:19.080 --> 00:16:21.420
No one asked you!

00:16:21.420 --> 00:16:22.750
What, me?

00:16:23.330 --> 00:16:25.500
I'm not that hungry right now.

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:26.790
What, why?!

00:16:26.790 --> 00:16:28.380
Let's go get something!

00:16:28.380 --> 00:16:30.210
I dunno, I'm just not.

00:16:31.580 --> 00:16:33.500
<i>That was close!</i>

00:16:33.710 --> 00:16:36.880
<i>We haven't talked in a while,
but he's still the same as ever.</i>

00:16:37.420 --> 00:16:40.290
<i>I'm sure even now, he'd see someone like me and-</i>

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:42.080
It's Ko, right?

00:16:42.670 --> 00:16:44.630
M...Mahiru-kun...

00:16:44.630 --> 00:16:46.460
Hey! Long time no see!

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:50.960
Just a few streets away and
there are a lot fewer people around.

00:16:51.630 --> 00:16:52.830
Yeah...

00:16:54.130 --> 00:16:56.670
U-um, is this okay?

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:58.710
Weren't you out with friends?

00:16:59.630 --> 00:17:01.210
Oh, it's fine.

00:17:01.210 --> 00:17:02.420
I told them what's up.

00:17:05.290 --> 00:17:07.710
And I mean, I'm surprised you knew it was me.

00:17:07.710 --> 00:17:08.960
It's been ages.

00:17:10.420 --> 00:17:12.000
Of course I could tell!

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:13.210
We're friends, aren't we?

00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:17.330
<i>"From what point are people friends?"</i>

00:17:17.710 --> 00:17:19.790
<i>is a question I always have,</i>

00:17:20.130 --> 00:17:24.330
<i>but I'm pretty certain that Akira and Mahiru-kun
were most definitely my friends.</i>

00:17:25.080 --> 00:17:27.920
<i>Still, Akira was a girl,</i>

00:17:27.920 --> 00:17:33.250
<i>and a part of me back in elementary school
wasn't too sure how to interact with her.</i>

00:17:34.040 --> 00:17:36.830
<i>On the other hand, things were easy with Mahiru-kun.</i>

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:39.540
<i>From my perspective...</i>

00:17:39.540 --> 00:17:44.420
<i>from anyone's perspective really, I'm sure of it.</i>

00:17:45.880 --> 00:17:47.790
<i>Mahiru-kun was perfect.</i>

00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:51.830
<i>He has good grades, excells at sports,</i>

00:17:51.830 --> 00:17:53.880
<i>and never hesitates to get up in front of people.</i>

00:17:54.290 --> 00:17:58.290
<i>All the teachers trust him, but he isn't too serious.</i>

00:17:59.170 --> 00:18:01.210
<i>To top it off, his family runs a flower shop.</i>

00:18:01.710 --> 00:18:03.460
<i>All of his factors are just so amazing.</i>

00:18:04.250 --> 00:18:06.750
<i>I'm sure nobody has anything bad
to say about Mahiru-kun.</i>

00:18:07.710 --> 00:18:12.000
<i>So being told I'm a friend of his
makes me super happy.</i>

00:18:14.130 --> 00:18:17.540
You have kind of a unique presence,
so I can tell right away, like,

00:18:17.540 --> 00:18:19.420
"Hey, that's Ko!"

00:18:20.540 --> 00:18:22.460
Y-you think so?

00:18:22.830 --> 00:18:25.420
You're the one who stands out.
I could spot you anywhere.

00:18:27.040 --> 00:18:30.540
I guess we always noticed each other
but never got the chance to talk, huh?

00:18:30.540 --> 00:18:31.960
Y-yeah, me too.

00:18:31.960 --> 00:18:33.790
I'm happy I get to see you for the first time in-

00:18:33.790 --> 00:18:36.080
This conversation's a little too corny for me.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.420
Whoa, you startled me!

00:18:38.420 --> 00:18:39.420
Yo.

00:18:39.420 --> 00:18:41.540
Are you heading home now?
It's awfully late.

00:18:41.540 --> 00:18:43.250
No, I just got up.

00:18:43.250 --> 00:18:44.540
That's awfully early!

00:18:44.710 --> 00:18:46.500
Is it early?

00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:49.130
Akira's sleep cycle is way out of whack.

00:18:49.130 --> 00:18:51.290
I defintiely don't want to hear that from you.

00:18:53.790 --> 00:18:56.380
You're skipping school and
fooling around with a girl at night?

00:18:56.380 --> 00:18:59.210
That's right!
Tell him, Mahiru!

00:18:59.210 --> 00:19:01.420
Tell him he should at least come to school.

00:19:01.670 --> 00:19:03.210
<i>What's the big deal?</i>

00:19:03.630 --> 00:19:06.000
What do you do with her, specifically?

00:19:06.460 --> 00:19:08.540
We go on walks, play video games...

00:19:11.460 --> 00:19:12.960
Spending time with her...

00:19:13.290 --> 00:19:14.540
Is it fun?

00:19:14.540 --> 00:19:16.080
Uh, yeah.

00:19:17.080 --> 00:19:18.290
I see.

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:22.500
Oh, sorry you two.

00:19:22.500 --> 00:19:23.920
I'm supposed to meet someone.

00:19:23.920 --> 00:19:25.130
They're already there.

00:19:25.670 --> 00:19:26.880
I should go.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:28.170
Oh, okay.

00:19:31.080 --> 00:19:32.080
Ko...

00:19:33.630 --> 00:19:36.080
Thanks, you've encouraged me a bit.

00:19:36.540 --> 00:19:37.750
See you!

00:19:41.670 --> 00:19:44.920
I don't know what just happened,
but Mahiru-kun thanked me.

00:19:45.380 --> 00:19:46.630
I'm so happy!

00:19:46.630 --> 00:19:49.880
You know, around Mahiru you really get corny.

00:19:49.880 --> 00:19:51.380
Wh-what do you mean?!

00:19:51.380 --> 00:19:52.920
I mean, it's Mahiru-kun!

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:55.710
Fine, fine, he's your role model.

00:19:55.710 --> 00:19:57.670
He's everyone's role model!

00:20:00.290 --> 00:20:02.130
Well, actually...

00:20:02.960 --> 00:20:05.080
there's this person I like...

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:10.080
I'm going to go home to sleep again.

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:12.880
You're looking for Nazuna Nanakusa, aren't you?

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:13.920
Yeah.

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:15.130
Goodnight.

